dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Morgan Hill quadrangle, Santa Clara County, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.

"The field work for this map was completed as Open File Report OF-73-59 while Tom Dibblee was with the U.S. Geological Survey. Where appropriate this map has recently been updated and revised by Tom."
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle MORGAN HILL, CA 1955, DMA 1658 II NW - Series V895, PHOTOREVISED 1980."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
